'''Fleet Ops''' was an element of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic's]] military during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. Along with the [[Logistics battalion]]s attached to the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]], it was responsible for the deployment of personnel and supplies to front-line units, under the central authority of the [[logistics center]] at [[Coruscant Command HQ]].

The name of Fleet Ops implies that it was specifically concerned with spacegoing fleet units, although it is not clear whether it was a preexisting element of the the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]], or a new organization established to deal specifically with the [[Assault ship/Legends|assault ships]] and other [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]] serving directly with the GAR.

'''Fleet Support''' was a branch of Fleet Ops dealing in refits, repairs and general maintenance of all [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|GAR]] spacegoing vessels during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was also responsible for maintaining various Fleet installations and ordnance depots, like [[Ord Mantell/Legends|Ord Mantell]] and Coruscant [[Fleet Support Depot]], throughout the galaxy.

